definitions.definition: A few silk threads or horsehairs , or a strip of linen etc., introduced beneath the skin by a knife or needle, so as to induce suppuration ; also, the issue so formed.

main_definition: ( medicine , agriculture ) A few silk threads or horsehairs , or a strip of linen etc., introduced beneath the skin by a knife or needle, so as to induce suppuration ; also, the issue so formed.
